            <p facs="#facs_1_r_1">
               <lb facs="#facs_1_r_tl_2" n="N001"/>would hide all traces of the method of his death - traces
               <lb facs="#facs_1_r_1_tl_1" n="N002"/>which for some reason must have pointed to him. Is all
               <lb facs="#facs_1_r_tl_3" n="N003"/>this not obvious?"</p>
            <p facs="#facs_1_r_2">
               <lb facs="#facs_1_r_2_tl_1" n="N001"/>could appear that <rs type="person" ref="#oldacre">Oldacre</rs>, who was a very excentres crature, and
               <lb facs="#facs_1_r_2_tl_3" n="N002"/>man without a friend in the world, had gone off taking his
               <lb facs="#facs_1_r_2_tl_2" n="N003"/>p
               <lb facs="#facs_1_r_2_tl_4" n="N004"/>ropers with him. Is all that not obvious?
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l" n="N005"/>his </p>
            <p facs="#facs_1_r_4">
               <lb facs="#facs_1_r_4_tl_2" n="N001"/>"It strikes me, my <rs type="person" ref="#lestrade">Lestrade</rs>, as being just a triple
               <lb facs="#facs_1_r_4_tl_1" n="N002"/>good
               <lb facs="#facs_1_r_tl_4" n="N003"/>too obvious" said <rs type="person" ref="#holmes">Holmes</rs> "You do not add imagination to your
               <lb facs="#facs_1_r_tl_5" n="N004"/>other great qualities, but if you could for a moment put yourself in
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_1" n="N005"/>one
               <lb facs="#facs_1_r_tl_6" n="N006"/>the place of a young man would you choose the very night after
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_3" n="N007"/>this
               <lb facs="#facs_1_r_4_tl_3" n="N008"/>the will had been made to commit your crime, would it not
               <lb facs="#facs_1_r_4_tl_4" n="N009"/>seem danerous to you to make so very close a relation between
               <lb facs="#facs_1_r_tl_7" n="N010"/>the two incidents. Again would you choose an occasion when
               <lb facs="#facs_1_r_4_tl_5" n="N011"/>you are known to be in the house, when a servant has let you in,
               <lb facs="#facs_1_r_4_tl_6" n="N012"/>and finally would you take great pains to conceal the body, and
               <lb facs="#facs_1_r_4_tl_7" n="N013"/>yet leave your own stick as a sign that you were the criminal.
               <lb facs="#facs_1_r_4_tl_8" n="N014"/>Confess, <rs type="person" ref="#lestrade">Lestrade</rs>, that all this is very unlikely"</p>
            <p facs="#facs_1_r_5">
               <lb facs="#facs_1_r_5_tl_1" n="N001"/>"As to the stick, Mr <rs type="person" ref="#holmes">Holmes</rs>, you know as well as I do
               <lb facs="#facs_1_r_5_tl_2" n="N002"/>that a criminal is often flurried and does things which a cool
               <lb facs="#facs_1_r_5_tl_3" n="N003"/>He was very likely apaid 170 back to the room.
               <lb facs="#facs_1_r_5_tl_4" n="N004"/>man would avoid. Give me another theory that would fet the facts"</p>
            <p facs="#facs_1_r_6">
               <lb facs="#facs_1_r_6_tl_1" n="N001"/>"I could very casily give you half a dozen" said
               <lb facs="#facs_1_r_6_tl_2" n="N002"/>for example
               <lb facs="#facs_1_r_6_tl_3" n="N003"/><rs type="person" ref="#holmes">Holmes</rs>
               <lb facs="#facs_1_r_6_tl_4" n="N004"/>"Here is a very possible and even probable one. I make</p></div>
